---
title: Herby Cherry-Glazed Chicken & Garlic Mash with Braised Balsamic Cabbage & Green Beans
description: Chicken, mash and veg, it doesn’t get much more classic than that! We’ve added a few surprises to jazz up this tried-and-true combo - flavourful garlic mashed in with the potatoes, a sweet cherry glaze on the chicken, and cabbage braised in a sweet and tangy balsamic sauce. Dig in!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
